# Lumio environment variables
# Development mode works without this file.
# Production mode requires real secrets and database credentials.

# Required in production only:
# JWT_SECRET=<run: openssl rand -base64 32>
# JWT_REFRESH_SECRET=<run: openssl rand -base64 32>
# DATABASE_URL=postgresql://user:password@host:5432/finflow

# User-managed integrations are configured in the UI:
# AI-compatible endpoint, SMTP, S3-compatible storage, WebDAV, IMAP, Telegram, and App URL.
# Env integration values are supported only as temporary bootstrap/fallback defaults.
